- move the .rp5rc file into your home dir
- edit .rp5rc to have the correct java library path
- plug in your kinect
- run: $ rp5 run k.rb

For Live Coding:
- run: $ rp5 live k.rb
- type this
$app.toggle_rgb
$app.tilt_up
etc.

More on Ruby-Processing Live Coding here: https://github.com/jashkenas/ruby-processing/wiki/Sketch-Watching-and-Live-Coding